Challenge Rules:

1. NO BAGS ALLOWED IN THE TEMPLE!!!

2. A player can not be challenged until they have been logged in for
   15 minutes.

3. Once a challenge has been issued, the player has 5 minutes to
   accept the challenge.

4. The fight will not start for at least 5 minutes after the challenge
   has been accepted.

5. Quiting the game is the same as forfeiting the challenge.

6. Too many forfeits will result in lowering of rank.

7. Challenge can only be issued to players ranked within 10 ranks
   below your rank.

8. Challenges can be issued to players no more than 25 ranks higher
   than your rank.

9. The Mortal Kombat Champion can only be challenged by the top 
   ten ranking players.
